### Base URL
@baseURL = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = {{token}}
@employeeId = {{employeeId}}
@teamId = {{teamId}}

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Register (New Org + Admin User)
POST {{baseURL}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orgName": "Test Company",
  "adminName": "Karthan",
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Login (Get JWT Token)
POST {{baseURL}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Paste token below after login:
# @token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1...

### Get Employees (Empty list initially)
GET {{baseURL}}/employees
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjIsIm9yZ0lkIjoyLCJpYXQiOjE3NjM3ODg3NTIsImV4cCI6MTc2MzgxNzU1Mn0.ehhkRhGeCSU9hp2p09xrp3zEixmBrxZvhiUX2Astk-c

